42:20.814 --> 42:24.542
[Marina speaking in Russian]

42:30.548 --> 42:31.652
You stop.

42:32.757 --> 42:34.552
I will never stop.

42:35.622 --> 42:38.797
[streetlamps buzzing]

42:44.182 --> 42:46.633
[door slams]

42:46.633 --> 42:49.256
