43:01.682 --> 43:04.720
- The inquiry has found
that Mr. Litvinenko

43:04.720 --> 43:06.653
was deliberately poisoned

43:06.653 --> 43:09.828
by Andrey Lugovoy
and Dmitry Kovtun.

43:11.278 --> 43:14.626
The inquiry has also found
that Lugovoy and Kovtun

43:14.626 --> 43:16.594
were acting on behalf of others

43:16.594 --> 43:19.597
when they poisoned
Mr. Litvinenko.

43:19.597 --> 43:21.529
There is a strong probability

43:21.529 --> 43:23.324
that they were acting
under the direction

43:23.324 --> 43:26.017
of the Russian domestic
security service,

43:26.017 --> 43:28.606
the Federal Security
Service, or FSB.

43:29.607 --> 43:31.609
And the inquiry has found

43:31.609 --> 43:35.682
that the FSB operation
to kill Mr. Litvinenko

43:35.682 --> 43:38.685
was probably approved
by Mr. Patrushev,

43:38.685 --> 43:41.446
the then head of the FSB,

43:41.446 --> 43:43.655
and by President Putin.

43:45.070 --> 43:47.901
