44:04.055 --> 44:05.953
Why you hide this from me?

44:10.026 --> 44:11.027
When are you due?

44:11.027 --> 44:11.856
- Any day now.

44:12.857 --> 44:13.789
A little boy.

44:14.962 --> 44:16.239
And, well,

44:17.585 --> 44:19.415
we were hoping...

44:19.415 --> 44:20.899
- Um, we were hoping,

44:22.004 --> 44:22.970
if you'd be so kind,

44:22.970 --> 44:25.317
as to give us your blessing, um,

44:26.664 --> 44:27.906
